ast.config

Interface ConfigFactory


  • public interface ConfigFactory

    A factory object that generates Config objects. Providers of new Config implementations should provide corresponding ConfigFactory implementations so that the new Config implementation can be installed in place of the platform-specific default implementation.

    This class is for Config implementers only. Normal users of the Config facility should have no need to consult this documentation.
